column5: Here’s a little video I made going to check out the shiner run. Bugs were terrible . If your going into the bush up here bring bug spray and lots of it. Worst bug year yet. Enjoy the video https://youtu.be/_KzEMjdILiQ
May be the worst year for bugs but the best year to reef on fish.
Yes one of the best years I’ve had for fishing in Red Lake. Some big hogs are being pulled from the lake.
